title: Woman In Lotus Position Dark Skin Tone
description: Depicts a woman with dark skin tone sitting in a meditative lotus position. It symbolizes peace, tranquility, yoga, meditation, and spiritual practice.
apple_vendor_description: Apple's depiction of a woman in the lotus position with a dark skin tone radiates peace and mindfulness. The illustration, rendered with Apple's signature glossy 3D effect and soft, rounded edges, shows the figure gracefully seated in meditation. Subtle gradients and realistic lighting lend a serene and grounded quality, making this emoji ideal for expressing tranquility, yoga, or moments of deep reflection.
